title: Converse x Decibel Collaboration: The Shrine talk rock and skateboarding
description: Fuzzy psych specialists The Shrine are causing waves in the rock world with their scuzzed out, throwback tunes. But they are just as comfortable ripping up pools -- for them the search is all the same. Catch up with the LA-based crew to see how skateboarding and rock and roll fuel their world. For more -- head to Decibelmagazine.com/Converse
